{"tid":2084418,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"甘肅北魏佛像慘遭「整容」 網民嘲笑似櫻桃小丸子爺爺","createTime":"2020-06-29T08:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T08:59:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bbcd659c7c40f8bdc1c5c0189974c47e3d99a9a1","tid":2084418,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2675000/2678107/1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2675000%2F2678107%2F1_1024.jpg&h=76f7470e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國是四大文明古國之一，長久以來，留下不少文物，但隨著時間的流逝，再加上天災人禍，不時都要進行修補，不過如果手藝不好情況可能更糟。近日，有網民發現甘肅省西和縣法鏡寺石窟的佛像經修復後，顯得相當滑稽，有人更嘲笑像動漫《櫻桃小丸子》中的中野爺爺。<br />\n<br />\n有網民發現甘肅省西和縣法鏡寺石窟的佛像經修復後，顯得相當滑稽<br />\n文化站站長汪娟奎解釋，當時村民發動捐款行動，聘請匠人進行修繕，修繕後並未改變佛像原貌<br />\n有人指 13 號窟北崖立佛是法鏡寺唯一保存完好的造像，確實面帶微笑，但也稱得上是法相莊嚴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2675000/2678107/6d3d46e9ly1gfwpwx4z1nj21400u04qp_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2675000%2F2678107%2F6d3d46e9ly1gfwpwx4z1nj21400u04qp_600.jpg&h=4ca2ee96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n甘肅的法鏡寺石窟現存 14 尊石窟佛像，建造於北魏太和年間，不過由於本身石質鬆散，加上風化及文革時期的破壞，所以至 1998 年時，開始重新塑造。近日有內地網民在微博發帖，發現佛像變得十分滑稽，之後相片在網絡瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2675000/2678107/aae51536bd5a1d529f299e70b65fe68a_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2675000%2F2678107%2Faae51536bd5a1d529f299e70b65fe68a_600.jpg&h=795dece9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文化站站長汪娟奎解釋，當時村民發動捐款行動，聘請匠人進行修繕。修繕後並未改變佛像原貌，僅是在修復時增加了佛像的顏色，而「笑」本來就是笑佛的特徵。不過此說法的正確性隨即被質疑，有人指 13 號窟北崖立佛是法鏡寺唯一保存完好的造像，確實面帶微笑，但也稱得上是法相莊嚴，至少不是滑稽逗趣。"},{"pid":"c310bcd84354c9450bb2dd0b202bb313c7192e40","tid":2084418,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:32:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2678107/%E7%94%98%E8%82%85%E5%8C%97%E9%AD%8F%E4%BD%9B%E5%83%8F%E6%85%98%E9%81%AD%E3%80%8C%E6%95%B4%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%8D%20%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%98%B2%E7%AC%91%E4%BC%BC%E6%AB%BB%E6%A1%83%E5%B0%8F%E4%B8%B8%E5%AD%90%E7%88%BA%E7%88%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2678107%2F%25E7%2594%2598%25E8%2582%2585%25E5%258C%2597%25E9%25AD%258F%25E4%25BD%259B%25E5%2583%258F%25E6%2585%2598%25E9%2581%25AD%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2595%25B4%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E3%2580%258D%2520%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2598%25B2%25E7%25AC%2591%25E4%25BC%25BC%25E6%25AB%25BB%25E6%25A1%2583%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25B8%25B8%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%2588%25BA%25E7%2588%25BA&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTdiuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=57c5d5cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2678107/%E7%94%98%E8%82%85%E5%8C%97%E9%AD%8F%E4%BD%9B%E5%83%8F%E6%85%98%E9%81%AD%E3%80%8C%E6%95%B4%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%8D%20%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%98%B2%E7%AC%91%E4%BC%BC%E6%AB%BB%E6%A1%83%E5%B0%8F%E4%B8%B8%E5%AD%90%E7%88%BA%E7%88%BA</a>"},{"pid":"9f3f44c0897a0a0eac3feedbceec53d3b2405872","tid":2084418,"uid":94828,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:35:57.000Z","msg":"呢個係撚小丸子爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fcdd86a2b40d5cbcdc0a3bf09fad8aaf4bf94ef","tid":2084418,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9f3f44c0897a0a0eac3feedbceec53d3b2405872","tid":2084418,"uid":94828,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:35:57.000Z","msg":"呢個係撚小丸子爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:59:46.000Z","msg":"如果講：似習近平<br />\n第日呢個像會唔會炸鳩咗佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad